-- Standard Chartered Said to Hire Haigh to Head Global Commodities Research
-- Chanyaporn Chanjaroen
-- 2010-07-23T14:42:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/standard-chartered-said-to-hire-haigh-to-head-global-commodities-research.html

          
          
             Standard Chartered Bank hired
 Michael Haigh  as global head of commodities research, according
to a person with direct knowledge of the appointment.  
 Haigh, formerly of K2 Advisors LLC, will be based in
Singapore and report to  Alex Barrett , head of client research,
the person said, declining to be identified by name because the
appointment hasnâ€™t been announced.  
